11. **Download page** - Plugin files, installation
12. **Checkout API** - Stripe integration
13. **Webhook API** - Subscription handling
14. **Final polish** - Animations, performance
15. **Documentation update** - Update CLAUDE.md

## Post-Completion

After all features complete and tests pass:
1. Run final comprehensive E2E test suite
2. Update `/Users/imorgado/SPLICE/CLAUDE.md` with:
